---
source: crates/test-framework/src/snapshot/mod.rs
description: "Query: tpch_simple_q4"
---
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                        |
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_quantity DESC NULLS FIRST, fetch=10                                                                                            |
|               |   Projection: avg(hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_tax), hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_linenumber, hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_quantity                                           |
|               |     Aggregate: groupBy=[[hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_linenumber, hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_quantity]], aggr=[[avg(hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_tax)]]                     |
|               |       BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                    |
|               |         TableScan: hadoop.tpch.lineitem projection=[l_linenumber, l_quantity, l_tax]                                                                        |
| physical_plan | SortPreservingMergeExec: [l_quantity@2 DESC], fetch=10                                                                                                      |
|               |   SortExec: TopK(fetch=10), expr=[l_quantity@2 DESC], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                          |
|               |     ProjectionExec: expr=[avg(hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_tax)@2 as avg(hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_tax), l_linenumber@0 as l_linenumber, l_quantity@1 as l_quantity] |
|               |       AggregateExec: mode=FinalPartitioned, gby=[l_linenumber@0 as l_linenumber, l_quantity@1 as l_quantity], aggr=[avg(hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_tax)]        |
|               |         CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                         |
|               |           RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([l_linenumber@0, l_quantity@1], 16), input_partitions=16                                                       |
|               |             AggregateExec: mode=Partial, gby=[l_linenumber@0 as l_linenumber, l_quantity@1 as l_quantity], aggr=[avg(hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_tax)]           |
|               |               RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(16), input_partitions=1                                                                         |
|               |                 BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                          |
|               |                   IcebergTableScan projection:[l_linenumber,l_quantity,l_tax] predicate:[]                                                                  |
|               |                                                                                                                                                             |
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
